data.description: About 20 minutes from Conway/Cabot/Sherwood, this home on almost 10 acres is a MUST SEE!  It has a stocked pond at the entrance to the property and the owner has successfully hunted deer and other wildlife on site.  The home is on a permanent foundation and has three bedrooms, two full baths, a built in desk area off of the dining room, large master closet and jetted tub.  There is also a cabin set back behind the home with a loft space, toilet, and area for a wood burning stove.  Three outbuildings sit near the front of the home with electricity hookup. Come check it out!
